<td>early 14th century</td>
<td>
<div class="floatright"><a href="/wiki/File:Mirall_de_Trobar.jpg" class="image" title="Mirall de Trobar.jpg"><img alt="" src="http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/en/thumb/7/71/Mirall_de_Trobar.jpg/75px-Mirall_de_Trobar.jpg" width="75" height="116" border="0" /></a></div>
