<td>"Little Chansonnier of Ripoll"</td>
<td>Anonymous</td>
<td>1346, Roussillon or Cerdagne</td>
<td>A <a href="/wiki/Chansonnier" title="Chansonnier">chansonnier</a> containing a unique grammar, including a catalogue of poetic genres, expands on the <i>Doctrina de compondre dictats</i> and the <i>Leys d'amors</i>.</td>
